Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill the bastard who ordered them to do this—Kida Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the eyes of someone who's prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:07.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean {\i1}that{\i0} Horada?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What Horada?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should tell you what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also prepared to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:16.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone contradict that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:19.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared to accept what you're\N about to see, no matter how horrible it may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:22.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:58.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugamine...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely about as bad as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the black biker shows herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, turn all these losers into dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Turn on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:33.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Ka-Kadota!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:12.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tricked someone with this disguise, then\N you should have been wary about adding new people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadota...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:14.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Togusa gave me this idea:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:25.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when Izumii got arrested, a guy named\N Horada was the only one to get away scot-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:32.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he rounded up about thirty of his friends, had everyone throw on some yellow, and they all snuck into your gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I left Yumasaki and Karisawa\N behind, since they're easily recognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we don't get to help out at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we are easily recognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to remember anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:48.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just that despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who broke Saki's leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who made Saki cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:00.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My gun... Where's my gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on breaking your skull open with that crowbar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado and Anri don't belong in this type of world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:19.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no reason for them to see a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.41,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:36.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty told me all about your and Sonohara's identities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugamine, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:46.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything. I get the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:48.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, don't force yourself to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:57.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably wouldn't have turned out like this if I'd just talked to you guys about what I was suffering through and worrying over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:02.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also felt like you were pulling away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell either of you about myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're both very important to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I've always been so close to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are absolutely perfect for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:36.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask a favor of you if you're going to take me to a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:42.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Raira General. I have a girl who's waiting for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:56.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I told him not to run away, but this time\N he did too good a job of facing things head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to know what a happy medium is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are these people...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're all in the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are certain things you can do when you don't have a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:12.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you tell them to disappear, they are who they are, so there's no way they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Horada's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Horada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Kida to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a van parked out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:32.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Togusa, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:34.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:39.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something to clean up. I'll leave Kida to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Horada, Higa's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Sh-Sh-She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's the black biker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, Horada?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we're going to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll escape somewhere and wait until things cool down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:18.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, once Izumii gets out of the pen, it'll be payback time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Horada, in front of us! In front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:31.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In front?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Heiwajima Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:45.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why's there a street sign in the middle of the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he still alive? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.82,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Horada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:09.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:18.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together, Horada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The black biker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Horada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve, coming that close to a police bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate traffic cops, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:06.01,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Horada and the others were arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:13.15,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they claimed that Heiwajima Shizuo\N destroyed their car, but their words fell upon deaf ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:22.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sonohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:49.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can finally get that reward from the Awakusu Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. However, I couldn't retrieve the bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:10:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been lucky if you'd killed Shizu-chan with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:05.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you used me to give Horada that information about Shizuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He would've died if you'd hit him in either the head or the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it is, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go home and live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...so you're Orihara Izaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Sonohara Anri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:44.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say Saika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want at this late hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let me slash you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:57.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why have you done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:08.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I had to give a reason for my\N actions, I guess it's because I love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:12.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I wanted to see the many faces that mankind has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Question time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:18.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was my answer just now the truth or a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll know...once I gain control of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:34.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly want to lead a happy, peaceful life, shouldn't you just slash everyone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:44.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, can you say that it's right to not make your feelings for either Mikado or Kida clear, despite knowing they're both attracted to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:50.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you just use your belief that you can't love others as an excuse to complacently accept how things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:58.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just using your assumption that you can't love others as an excuse to be complacent with how things currently are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika loves people in your stead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not like I got to be Shizu-chan's rival by just pretending to fight with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have given this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you right now that I won't use it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just whom should I use it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:36.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that couple walking by over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:41.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't cause you too much emotional pain, since you can't love others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:46.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd known for a long time that Higa had fallen victim to the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I told him to get this gun back for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to declare war on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:58.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I deeply love people, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd ever hand them over to some sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People are my playthings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:11.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you can have Shizu-chan; I don't need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm praying for you to cut him up like a fish as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:32.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got hit with a pretty good punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:57.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have something to tell you, but you're not going to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cowardly it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...I know I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love my own cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:12.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember Masaomi's girlfriend? She called my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:16.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She told us all about you and what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's truly in love with Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's turned her back on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Saki, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Izaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ransack this town too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:39.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon, I told you I truly love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to trick me with that logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, you just don't want to lose to Shizuo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have a Shizuo complex, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't realize just how much those around you can tell what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...Simon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:02.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like a totally different person when you're speaking Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who told Horada about Mikado, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vindictive people like you are just scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...whenever someone reacts exactly the way I expect them to,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there are always people like Shizuo and Simon \Nwho turn those expectations on their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:29.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll never ever stop loving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely how I'm able to keep working this piece of shit job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fun it makes me vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:43.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again, but I'm pretty sure that humanity hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:56.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You never came, did you, Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:05.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just kept calling Izaya, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya laughed as he showed me his phone's incoming call history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:18.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you had come, not much would've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least you didn't get injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:24.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:37.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Saki ever see in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're oddly obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:46.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Karisawa and the others told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool, Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've known that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:56.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's something I have to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I got caught by those people on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:05.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya told me it'd all stop if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, I went by myself to their meeting place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:16.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And afterwards, Izaya told people about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He told you to, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He told you to keep pretending you couldn't walk so he could reign me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably wanted to turn me into his pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have ESP, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:36.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever disobeyed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can finally say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't come save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:40.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:48.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, don't break up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool, Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an absolute idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you close your eyes to at least one of my faults?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know you have one, then fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fix it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:18.08,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days later, Masaomi disappeared along with Mikajima Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:23.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They notified the school that they were dropping out and just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.83,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday life changed for the three of us that had been living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:33.42,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, the city hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Russia Sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.05,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither has he,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.05,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,nor have they,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.13,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,or them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.26,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,or him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.64,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,or him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tranquil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:52.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there's internal strife even amongst the remaining people from the Blue Squares,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Yellow Scarves have also quieted down a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:19:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then there's no reason to worry about anyone coming after Anri or Mikado for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai... What's with that bold change of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to provoke me like that, I've got to take a shower and prepare some bed sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:22.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, usually you'd give me a Hell Stab \Nsomewhere around here or pinch my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually am trying to provoke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.13,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:35.15,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never regain the everyday life that we've lost, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:39.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I loved Kida...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why I feel so lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really...understand that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.93,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars are this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:56.74,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Various people come and go, without being dyed a certain color.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.74,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always something happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:06.85,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There are always people hating and loving each other, cultivating friendships, and passing others by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:16.96,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a city will continue to exist as long as there are people around, the Dollars will also continue to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.40,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.43,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,'Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.51,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.35,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we have a new person, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.37,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.16,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,nice to meet you. I'm Bacula.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.62,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanra invited me to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:35.00,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, I met him through the Internet, but did you as well, Bacula?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.37,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we know each other from RL.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:40.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,We're like business partners!\N At least that's the front we put up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:40.55,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Kya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.30,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to die, Kanra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.41,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a harsher quip than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.71,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.84,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.38,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanra was being really annoying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:49.22,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.31,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Bacula,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.76,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,please excuse me if I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.15,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.49,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.49,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It...It'd be great if you'd just say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:09.49,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You've met me in RL, so please tell\N everyone what's so charming about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.33,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The square root of three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.29,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:15.25,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to express your charm with points, \Nit'd be the square root of three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:19.95,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in other words, I'm so beautiful that you can't evenly divide me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.97,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,More like you're too difficult for elementary \Nschool kids, so we shouldn't show you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.14,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.30,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,this is it for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.51,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:31.84,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.84,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.97,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Bacula!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.60,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.39,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.48,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.34,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,'Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.27,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.27,ASS Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(205,150)}Bacula has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:48.19,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A place to come home to and an everyday life that's been lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...also exists on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi will definitely come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:22:00.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's give him crap when he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pretend to be really mad at him as a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us will do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:10.99,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think it's mysterious even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I also get the feeling it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it was something that changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:19.69,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, it seems like nothing's changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.73,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something very, very strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and, at the same time, something everyone experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:28.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened here in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
